<T>__{cut to low angle shot :}
<A>__{of the procession making its way past the camera. black robed and cowled, the sinister figures look like heavily armed monks. these are the forces of darkness. together they are straining at several heavy hawsers that rise in long arcs up to a huge metal cage floating above and behind the procession. binding the cage are metal straps to which ropes are attached. inside is the girl still enveloped in gossamer which billows as if there were a breeze in constant attendance.}
